WWW-NicoVideo version 0.03
==========================

This module allows you to get information from Nico Nico Video service
(http://www.nicovideo.jp/) and also allows you to search from it.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

  perl Makefile.PL
  make
  make test
  make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  - libwww-perl (LWP)
  - Web::Scraper
  - Class::Accessor

